tor : my download utility script:

usage: tor [-h] [-d] [-l] [-c] [-p] [-v] [-a FILENAME] [-r ID]
           [--input INPUT_DIRECTORY] [--output OUTPUT_DIRECTORY] [--port PORT]
           [--ext EXT]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -d, --download        download all file from the input directory
  -l, --list            display all download tasks
  -c, --clear           remove all finished tasks
  -p, --purge           purge all downloadtasks
  -v, --version         version
  -a FILENAME, --add FILENAME
                        download file specified
  -r ID, --remove ID    remove download task specified by id
  --input INPUT_DIRECTORY
                        update input configuration variable
  --output OUTPUT_DIRECTORY
                        update output configuration variable
  --port PORT           update port configuration variable
  --ext EXT             update ext configuration variable
